          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Measurement of gamma-ray spectra obtained",
                " at disintegration of giant dipole resonance  of  the",
                " final  nuclei  31P  and  32S  was  made in identical",
                " conditions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " With  volume of 100 cm**3 placed at a distance",
                " of 35 cm from the beam axis.  Energy  resolution  is",
                " 3.5 keV for gamma-rays with energy 1.332 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To obtain  the  absolute  value  of  integral   cross",
                " sections   the   relative   method   was  used:  the",
                " experimental gamma-spectra were compared  with  well",
                " known spectrum (gamma,x gamma') reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Errors of this experiment were summed as  statistical",
                " errors   of   the  experimental  gamma  spectra  and",
                " probabilities of gamma transitions in final nuclei."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The aim  of this work was to estimate the probability",
                " of semidirect disintegration in partial photonuclear",
                " channels  for  23Na  nucleus. The  integrated  cross",
                " section for 23Na(gamma,p(I)) and 23Na(gamma,n(I))",
                " reactions and the semidirect components were obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
